snippet.title: One Minute🕓  - Trailer
snippet.description:
New Game❗
Introducing One Minute ! 🕓

Wishlist it now : https://store.steampowered.com/app/3301260/One_Minute/

One minute is a game developed by a solo developer of our team !

Dive into a frenetic chaos with One Minute, a fast and addictive roguelite! Unlock varied mini-games, collect cursor skins, and improve your scores to shine in the global leaderboard.

#gamedev #indiedev #indiegame #solodev #godot
